ProtoDefines:
. "If $t_0>0$, then the solution of the initial value problem 
   \begin{equation} ay''+by'+cy=\delta(t-t_0), \quad 
   y(0)=0,\quad y'(0)=0, \end{equation} is defined to be $$ 
   y=u(t-t_0)w(t-t_0), $$ where $$ w={\cal L}^{-1}\left(1\over 
   as^2+bs+c\right). $$"
